This code is intended to be an implementation of a paper that i am working on. This paper aims to propose theories needed to have an automated policy insertion and verification for ML. And this project is an implementation of that project.
The paper, the code, the documentation, credits (the initial code is from ocaml: http://caml.inria.fr/pub/docs/u3-ocaml/ocaml-ml.html and necessary open source license will be completed in time!

Hope you enjoy this and find it useful!
Arash Afshar
